    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when in 1927, '28-- no, no earlier-- 1923, '24, '25-- when people were paid as workers, they would leave the moment after they were paid and run to-- to the grocery store so that they could then buy grocery before the money was worthless the next day.",
      "word_count": 48
